This repository contains GUI elements for the vcswrapper package (https://github.com/forste/haskellVCSWrapper).
systems. Currently git, mercurial and svn are implemented.

Installing:

Currently you will need ghc 7.0.4 to install this package.
Additionally to install the related gtk packages you will need native gtk packages.

Hackage:

The package can be found on hackage: http://hackage.haskell.org/package/vcsgui.


